data.title: Remembering Tap Dancer Gene Kelly (1912-1996)
data.meta_description:
A tribute, profile, and fan site for
legendary tap dancer Gene Kelly.
data.text:
STAGE NAME: Gene Kelly

FULL NAME: Eugene Curran Kelly

DATE OF BIRTH: August 23, 1912

PLACE OF BIRTH: East Liberty, Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania, USA

DATE OF DEATH: February 2, 1996

PLACE OF DEATH: Beverly Hills, California, United States

WIFE 1941-1957: Betsy Blair

WIFE 1960 until she died: Jeanne Coyne

WIFE 1990 until he died: Patricia Ward

Videos of Gene Kelly Tap Dancing A collection of freemonoine videos of Gene Kelly tap dancing.
